constraint: The date shall contain two hyphens.
If there is at least one hyphen, the part before the hyphen shall be a number between 0 and 2025.
result: (let ((first-hyphen (str.indexof s "-" 0))) (=> (not (= first-hyphen -1)) (let ((before-first-hyphen (str.substr s 0 first-hyphen))) (and (>= (str.to.int before-first-hyphen) 0) (<= (str.to.int before-first-hyphen) 2025))))))

constraint: If there are at least two hyphens, the part after the first hyphen but before the second hyphen shall be a number between 1 and 12.
result: (let ((first-hyphen (str.indexof s "-" 0)) (second-hyphen (str.indexof s "-" (+ (str.indexof s "-" 0) 1)))) (=> (not (= second-hyphen -1)) (let ((between-hyphens (str.substr s (+ first-hyphen 1) (- second-hyphen first-hyphen 1)))) (and (>= (str.to.int between-hyphens) 1) (<= (str.to.int between-hyphens) 12))))))

constraint: If there are at least two hyphen, The part after the second hyphen shall be a number between 1 and 31.
result: (let ((second-hyphen (str.indexof s "-" (+ (str.indexof s "-" 0) 1)))) (=> (not (= second-hyphen -1)) (let ((after-second-hyphen (str.substr s (+ second-hyphen 1) (- (str.len s) second-hyphen 1)))) (and (>= (str.to.int after-second-hyphen) 1) (<= (str.to.int after-second-hyphen) 31))))))
